Programming: C++, Python, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, React •AI & ML: LangChain, LangGraph, OpenAI ,RAG, MCP, Fine-tuning, NLP •Databases: MongoDB, PostgreSQL •Tools: Git, VS Code, Postman, MongoDB Compass •Frameworks: Bootstrap, FastAPI, FastMCP English | Hindi

Aspiring Computer Science graduate with hands-on experience in Generative AI, RAG-based systems, LangChain, and Model Context Protocol. Skilled in designing and deploying production-ready AI chatbots with context-aware responses using OpenAI models and vector databases (MongoDB/PostgreSQL). Strong foundation in prompt engineering, conversation tracking, and full-stack UI development. Passionate about leveraging AI and emerging technologies to solve real-world problems and continuously improve system performance in collaborative environments.

Developed production-ready AI chatbots using LangChain, OpenAI models (text-embedding-3-small, gpt-4.1-mini), and MongoDB to respond accurately to client-provided documents in real time. •Built secure, client-facing web UI (HTML/CSS, authentication) for users to log in, interact with the bot, and review/update responses; maintained conversation history for each user session. •Implemented RAG-based retrieval, generating embeddings for user queries, fetching top relevant chunks, and incorporating conversation context for better responses. •Optimized prompts and request handling for high accuracy and safe multi-user usage in live environments; monitored system performance and reliability. •Conducted research and database benchmarking (MongoDB vs PostgreSQL) for vector search efficiency and performed model fine-tuning to improve live system response quality.

Multi-Modal RAG Chatbot, Backend Built a Streamlit-based chatbot using RAG architecture for interactive PDF querying. Extracted text, tables, and images using unstructured and generated embeddings for context-aware responses. Tech: Python, Streamlit, OpenAI API, PyMuPDF, pandas

Intelligent Train Booking Agent Developed an AI conversational agent to automate train bookings via natural language queries — including data fetch, seat check, and payment simulation. Tech: FastAPI, LangGraph, Razorpay API, Python

MCP Server for Claude AI Integrated a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server with Claude Desktop (local & remote) to enable real-time tool use and data access. Implemented an Expense Tracker feature as a sample tool. Tech: FastMCP, FastAPI, Python, Claude AI
